## Naming Evaluation (First Priority)

**Current function name**: `nextGeneration`
- Purpose: Computes the next generation of cells based on Game of Life rules
- Assessment: Name clearly reveals intent - it returns the next generation
- Decision: Keep `nextGeneration` - name is accurate and idiomatic

## Current Code Mass Calculation

```typescript
export function nextGeneration(cells: Cell[]): Cell[] {
  return cells.filter(([x, y]) => {
    const neighbors = cells.filter(([cx, cy]) => {
      const dx = cx - x;
      const dy = cy - y;
      return (dx !== 0 || dy !== 0) && Math.abs(dx) <= 1 && Math.abs(dy) <= 1;
    }).length;
    return neighbors === 2 || neighbors === 3;
  });
}
```

